docs.abstract: Vandal poisoned Auburn's mighty Toomer Oaks after 2012 football season, but he did not kill what trees represented; football fans see symmetry between oaks and two miracle plays that sealed two victories in the final minutes and how they propelled Auburn to the Bowl Championship Series title game.
